  "summary": "AlpenTech GmbH (Graz, Austria) Q3 2025 quarterly financial report showing strong performance with consolidated revenue of EUR 12.4 million (+15.8% YoY), EBITDA of EUR 2.6 million (21.0% margin), and net income of EUR 1.5 million (12.1% margin). Industrial Automation led growth at EUR 5.6 million (+24.4%) with 87 active customers. Predictive Maintenance grew 20.0% to EUR 4.2 million, bolstered by the AlpenPredict Edge product launch. Engineering Consulting declined 3.7% to EUR 2.6 million as part of strategic shift. Cash position reached EUR 8.9 million. Full-year revenue guidance EUR 47-49 million. Confidential board minutes reveal two acquisition targets (SimuTech EUR 3.8M, TwinFlow EUR 1.4M). Contains sensitive compensation benchmarks and employee PII. Marked DO NOT DISTRIBUTE."
